# Workspace {{ workspace_name }}

Branch: `{{ branch }}`
Base branch: `{{ base_branch }}`
Application path: `code/{{ app_subpath }}`

This directory is an Angee workspace, not an agent. Services can mount it with:

```yaml
mounts:
  - workspace://{{ workspace_name }}:/workspace
```

The `code/` directory is materialized by the operator from the stack-level
`django-angee` source. If `chain_root` is enabled, the inner stack lives at:

```text
code/{{ app_subpath }}/.angee
```
